quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  2,38,hum ne farmaya ke tum sab yahan se utar jao jab tumahray paas meri taraf se hadaayat puhanche to ( is ki pairwi karna ke ) jinhon ne meri hadaayat ki pairwi ki un ko nah kuch khauf hoga aur nah woh ghumnaak hon ge
  2,39,"aur jinhon ne ( is ko ) qubool nahkiya aur hamari aayton ko jhtlaya, woh dozakh mein jaane walay hain ( aur ) woh hamesha is mein rahen ge"
  2,40,ae Yaqoob ki aulaad! mere woh ahsaan yaad karo jo mein ne tum par kiye they aur is iqraar ko poora karo jo tum ne mujh sekiya tha. mein is iqraar ko poora karoon ga jo mein ne tum sekiya tha aur mujhi se drtay raho
  2,41,"aur jo kitaab mein ne ( apne rasool Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam par ) nazil ki hai jo tumhari kitaab torat ko sacha kehti hai, is par imaan lao aur is se munhkar awwal nah bano, aur meri aayton mein ( tahreef kar ke ) un ke badlay thori si qeemat ( yani dunyawi manafat ) nah haasil karo, aur mujhi se khauf rakho"
  2,42,"aur haq ko baatil ke sath nah mlao, aur sachhi baat ko jaan boojh kar nah chupao"
  2,43,aur namaz parha karo aur zakaat diya karo aur ( khuda ke agay ) jhuknay walon ke sath jhuka karo
  2,44,"( yeh )kiya ( aqal ki baat hai ke ) tum logon ko neki karne ko kehte ho aur apne tain faramosh kiye dete ho, halaank tum kitaab ( khuda ) bhi parhte ho.kiya tum samajte nahi ?"
  2,45,"aur ( ranj wa takleef mein ) sabr aur namaz se madad liya karo aur be shak namaz giran hai, magar un logon par ( giran nahi ) jo ijaz karne walay hain"
  2,46,aur jo yaqeen kiye hue hain ke woh apne perwar-digaar se milnay walay hain aur is ki taraf lout kar jaane walay hain
  2,47,"ae Yaqoob ki aulaad! mere woh ahsaan yaad karo, jo mein ne tum par kiye they aur yeh ke mein ne tum ko Jahan ke logon par fazeelat bakhsh thi"
  2,48,aur is din se daro jab koi kisi ke kuch kaam nah aeye aur nah kisi ki sifarish Manzoor ki jaye aur nah kisi se kisi terhan ka badla quboolkiya jaye aur nah log ( kisi aur terhan ) madad haasil kar saken
